{"tid":1643311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信向Now新聞反映意見，停止引述「暴徒」一詞","createTime":"2019-10-10T05:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T12:13:13.000Z","uid":101392,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3129e9d69fe34869778fffeb97abb20f11c98786","tid":1643311,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:32:45.000Z","msg":"留意到NOW新聞經常對黑警、政府嘅聲明字眼照單全收，就算係間接引述都叫市民做「暴徒」，無加引號，<br />\n<br />\n但咁樣其實違反新聞中立、違反無罪假定同埋涉嫌妨礙司法公正，<br />\n<br />\n一日未判決，一日都係無辜市民，<br />\n<br />\n就算報導殺人犯，都唔可以直接叫殺人犯，要叫「疑犯、疑兇、涉嫌謀殺嘅男子」<br />\n<br />\n除非直接引述（要加引號），否則應該以中立嘅字眼譬如「示威者」、「市民」取代，否則會喺將來陪審團心中預先造成壞印象<br />\n<br />\n其實係政府、黑警唔應該用「暴徒」呢個字眼，但係向政府投訴都多餘，唯有靠傳媒界把關<br />\n<br />\n/<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=365637\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365637&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Emz2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=effb6517\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365637&h=04bf80be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=365637</a><br />\n<br />\n警方表示留意到有人在社交媒體散播謠言，聲稱周二晚上有警員假扮<span style=\"color: red;\">暴徒</span>，進入港鐵上水站內破壞設施，警方澄清，因應近日有<span style=\"color: red;\">暴徒</span>在港鐵站進行破壞作調查，在收到相關消息後，曾調派便裝警員進入上水站內執行任務，指所有警員絕不會進行任何違法行為，會繼續按實際需要，採用不同方式打擊罪案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=365513&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365513%26refer%3D&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Emz2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=6bd00dad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365513%26refer%3D&h=3c16f2b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=365513&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n警方表示六月至今共拘捕2363人，過去四日拘捕241人，其中77人涉嫌干犯禁蒙面法。警方形容過去四日，<span style=\"color: red;\">暴徒</span>的破壞升級，有200間店舖受損，行為比過往野蠻及兇殘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=365433&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365433%26refer%3D&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Emz2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=1042a6f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365433%26refer%3D&h=0dbbb5ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=365433&amp;refer=</a><br />\n政府稱，蒙面<span style=\"color: red;\">暴徒</span>在多區堵路和縱火，大肆破壞商舖及港鐵站等，嚴重破壞社會秩序，不少商舖及公共設施被迫提早關門，又稱港鐵員工已盡力搶修，連日車站仍繼續遭受大規模破壞，令港鐵服務受影響，市民對周二如何上班上學感到焦慮，形容暴徒的行為無法無天，剝奪其他市民正常生活的權利，特區政府予以強烈譴責。/"},{"pid":"9bb6e18a5dfb858ac7e77bf00ec5db1afed16631","tid":1643311,"uid":101392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:36:04.000Z","msg":"漫大學生會會長方仲賢：「我們沒有讓步空間，有一千個<span style=\"color: red;\">義士</span>走上街頭，他們因為你推這條惡法出來，因為他們反抗這惡法而坐監，這是不合理。你撒回這條例即是認錯，為何我們示威者、<span style=\"color: red;\">義士</span>要因為你做錯的事而被控入罪。」<br />\n<br />\n佢報導「義士」呢個字係直接引述說話嗰陣先用<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=361634&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361634%26refer%3D&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Emz2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=ab66d370\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361634%26refer%3D&h=5d709a78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=361634&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"61d0a9415233773b12d28d2b7f81ef3ba58ab806","tid":1643311,"uid":288670,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:36:42.000Z","msg":"Now 已經變緊下一個cctvb"},{"pid":"dda405d229e18ce23e410a51321b3d4e96884f9c","tid":1643311,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:40:39.000Z","msg":"用「暴徒」形容返警察，同佢玩文字遊戲"},{"pid":"5641f977ffd7edf47f009b9ebcbe383531ce8914","tid":1643311,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:46:11.000Z","msg":"要打篇罐頭信叫巴打們炸佢email<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e54f0f46aba7532730b089525f13e34ec8e9cd","tid":1643311,"uid":283764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:48:51.000Z","msg":"now 最近d街頭訪問多左反對示威者既意見，唔肯定係now變左定受訪市民真係多左反對者。"},{"pid":"5b51197e3e0e06d88cb26c80b39d2348b01ecb1c","tid":1643311,"uid":23067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5e54f0f46aba7532730b089525f13e34ec8e9cd","tid":1643311,"uid":283764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:48:51.000Z","msg":"now 最近d街頭訪問多左反對示威者既意見，唔肯定係now變左定受訪市民真係多左反對者。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:50:12.000Z","msg":"覺得係造假"},{"pid":"77840adabd4b03d5df34897e6f9cd80ea30bab99","tid":1643311,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94c23091014af1599d6b2ad115367ee05fe2d49","tid":1643311,"uid":194399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T12:13:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}